msgstr "Število možnih igralcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>One</para>"
msgstr "<para>Eden</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kreversi; is a simple one player strategy game played against the computer. "
"The playing field is an 8 by 8 square board divided into 64 squares. The "
"game pieces used are two sided stones, where each side has its own, "
"distinctive color. If a piece is captured by an opposing player, that piece "
"is turned over to reveal the color of that player. A winner is declared when "
"one player has more pieces of his own color on the board and there are no "
"more possible moves."
msgstr ""
"&kreversi; je preprosta strateška igra za enega igralca, ki se igra proti "
"računalniku. Igralno polje je plošča velikosti 8 krat 8, razdeljena na 64 "
"polj. Uporabljeni igralni deli so dvostranski kamni, kjer ima vsaka stran "
"svojo značilno barvo. Če figuro ujame nasprotni igralec, se ta figura obrne, "
"da se razkrije barva tega igralca. Zmagovalec je razglašen, ko ima en "
"igralec na plošči več kosov svoje barve in ni več možnih potez."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Get control over the majority of squares on the board."
msgstr "Pridobite nadzor nad večino polj na plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kreversi; loads directly into the <guilabel>New game</guilabel> dialog "
"where you select the game mode, &ie; play against the computer or another "
"human player. As a first player you have the right to move first."
msgstr ""
"&kreversi; naloži neposredno v pogovorno okno <guilabel>Nova igra</"
"guilabel>, kjer izberete način igre, &ie;. igrajte proti računalniku ali "
"drugemu človeškemu igralcu. Kot prvi igralec imate pravico do prve poteze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default the human player always has a right to the first move."
msgstr "Privzeto ima človeški igralec vedno pravico do prve poteze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, imagine yourself that with each move your stone has to hop (jump) over "
"the enemy's one (or ones, as there might be more than one stone). Yet, your "
"stone does not relocate after the move, instead a new stone is placed on the "
"board onto where your stone would have appeared if it indeed could jump. "
"Once the move is done, all the enemy stones that you jump over, become yours "
"and change their color respectively."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj pa si predstavljajte, da mora vaš kamen z vsako potezo preskočiti "
"(preskočiti) sovražnikov kamen (ali ene, saj je kamnov lahko več). Vendar se "
"vaš kamen po premiku ne premakne, namesto tega se na ploščo postavi nov "
"kamen na mesto, kjer bi se vaš kamen pojavil, če bi res lahko skočil. Ko je "
"poteza opravljena, vsi sovražni kamni, ki jih preskočite, postanejo vaši in "
"spremenijo svojo barvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every single move you do in &kreversi; has to be done in this manner. And "
"you can jump your stones vertically, horizontally and diagonally. But, in "
"case there is nowhere to jump, your turn will automatically skip."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka poteza, ki jo naredite v &kreversi; je treba narediti na ta način. "
"Svoje kamne lahko skačete navpično, vodoravno in diagonalno. Toda v primeru, "
"da ni kam skočiti, bo vaša poteza samodejno preskočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same rule applies to your enemy. If there is no possibility to make a "
"move the turn is skipped."
msgstr ""
"Enako pravilo velja za vašega sovražnika. Če ni možnosti za potezo, se "
"njegova poteza preskoči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea here is to fill the board with the stones of your own color. The "
"player who manages to conquer the most of the game board is announced the "
"winner."
msgstr ""
"Ideja je, da ploščo napolnite s kamni svoje barve. Igralec, ki mu uspe "
"osvojiti večji del igralne plošče, je razglašen za zmagovalca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Basics"
msgstr "Osnove igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A move consists of outflanking your opponents stone(s), then flipping the "
"outflanked stone(s) to reveal your color. A move is performed by placing the "
"mouse pointer over the desired square then &LMB; click."
msgstr ""
"Poteza je sestavljena iz obdajanja nasprotnikovega kamna z boka, nato pa "
"obračanja obdanega kamna, da se razkrije vaša barva. Premik se izvede tako, "
"da kazalec miške postavite na želeno polje in nato &LMB; kliknete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To outflank means to place a stone on the board so that your opponent's "
"row(s) of stone(s) is bordered at each end by a stone of your color. A row "
"may be made up of one or more stones."
msgstr ""
"Obdati pomeni postaviti kamen na desko tako, da nasprotnikova vrsta kamnov "
"na obeh koncih obdaja kamen vaše barve. Vrstica je lahko sestavljena iz "
"enega ali več kamnov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game starts with the <guilabel>New game</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr "Igra se začne s pogovornim oknom <guilabel>Nova igra</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kreversi; Game Mode Selection</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kreversi; Izbira igralnega načina</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kreversi; Game Mode Selection</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kreversi; Izbira igralnega načina</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Mode Selection"
msgstr "Izbira igralnega načina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see a demo of the game select <guilabel>Computer</guilabel> for both "
"players."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled predstavitve igre izberite <guilabel>Računalnik</guilabel> za oba "
"igralca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each player automatically has two stones placed in the center four squares "
"of the board in the following pattern:"
msgstr ""
"Vsak igralec ima samodejno postavljena dva kamna na sredino štirih polj "
"plošče po naslednjem vzorcu:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kreversi; opening position</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kreversi; začetni položaj</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kreversi; opening position</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kreversi; začetni položaj</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Board Layout"
msgstr "Postavitev plošče"

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Menu Bar</interface> contains several choices of drop-down "
"menus. These are <guimenu>Game</guimenu>, <guimenu>Move</guimenu>, "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu>, <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu>. Click with the &LMB; or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>the underlined letter</keycap></keycombo> to show the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Menijska vrstica</interface> vsebuje več izbir spustnih menijev. "
"To so <guimenu>Igra</guimenu>, <guimenu>Premik</guimenu>, <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu>, <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>. "
"Kliknite z &LMB; ali <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>podčrtano črko</"
"keycap></keycombo> za prikaz spustnega menija."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides the player with icon shortcuts for commonly used actions. These are "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-new.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>New</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Undo</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"games-hint.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Hint</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-lastmoves.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Show Last Move</"
"guiicon>, and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-"
"legalmoves.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"<guiicon>Show Legal Moves</guiicon>. Place the mouse pointer over any of "
"these icons and click with the &LMB; to activate."
msgstr ""
"Predvajalniku ponuja bližnjice do ikon za pogosto uporabljena dejanja. To so "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-new.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Novo</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Razveljavi</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"games-hint.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Namig</guiicon>, "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"actions-lastmoves.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Pokaži zadnjo "
"potezo</guiicon> in <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"actions-legalmoves.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject "
"> <guiicon>Pokaži zakonite poteze</guiicon>. Kazalec miške postavite na "
"katero koli od teh ikon in kliknite z &LMB; za aktiviranje."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Board"
msgstr "Igralna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consists of a 8 by 8 square board divided into 64 squares."
msgstr "Sestavljen je iz plošče velikosti 8 krat 8, razdeljene na 64 polj."

#. Tag: interface
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status Bar"
msgstr "Statusna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays whose turn it is. As well as a drop-down box to choose the level of "
"difficulty."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje, kdo je na vrsti. Kot tudi spustno polje za izbiro težavnostne "
"stopnje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Pravila igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "You always move first."
msgstr "Vi se vedno premaknete prvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If on your turn you cannot outflank and flip at least one opposing stone, "
"your turn is forfeited and your opponent moves again. However, if a move is "
"available to you, you may not forfeit your turn."
msgstr ""
"Če na potezi ne morete obdati in obrniti vsaj enega nasprotnega kamna, je "
"vaša poteza izgubljena in vaš nasprotnik se znova premakne. Vendar, če vam "
"je na voljo poteza, ne smete izgubiti svojega reda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A stone may outflank any number of stones in one or more rows in any number "
"of directions at the same time - horizontally, vertically or diagonally. A "
"row is defined as one or more stones in a continuous straight line."
msgstr ""
"Kamen lahko obda poljubno število kamnov v eni ali več vrstah v poljubnem "
"številu smeri hkrati - vodoravno, navpično ali diagonalno. Vrstica je "
"opredeljena kot en ali več kamnov v neprekinjeni ravni črti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may not skip over your own color stone to outflank an opposing stone."
msgstr ""
"Ne smete preskočiti svojega barvnega kamna, da bi obdali nasprotni kamen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stones may only be outflanked as a direct result of a move and must fall in "
"the direct line of the stone placed down."
msgstr ""
"Kamni se lahko obdajo samo kot neposredna posledica poteze in morajo pasti v "
"direktno linijo kamna, ki je postavljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All stones outflanked in any one move must be flipped, even if it is to the "
"player's advantage not to flip them."
msgstr ""
"Vse kamne, ki so obdani v kateri koli potezi, je treba obrniti, tudi če je v "
"korist igralca, da jih ne obrne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a stone is placed on a square, it can never be moved to another square "
"later in the game."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kamen postavljen na polje, ga pozneje v igri nikoli več ni mogoče "
"premakniti na drugo polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it is no longer possible for either player to move, the game is over. "
"Stones are then counted and the player with the majority of his or her color "
"discs on the board is declared the winner."
msgstr ""
"Ko se nobeden od igralcev ne more več premikati, je igre konec. Nato se "
"preštejejo kamni in igralec z večino svojih barvnih plošč na plošči je "
"razglašen za zmagovalca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is possible for a game to end before all 64 squares are filled."
msgstr "Možno je, da se igra konča, preden je zapolnjenih vseh 64 polj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to place stones on the corners whenever possible. Your opponent cannot "
"outflank these stones."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite postaviti kamne na vogale, kadar koli je to mogoče. Vaš nasprotnik "
"ne more obdati teh kamnov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Avoid placing stones on one of the three neighbor fields of a corner unless "
"you are absolutely sure that your opponent will not be able to put a stone "
"on a corner."
msgstr ""
"Izogibajte se postavljanju kamnov na eno od treh sosednjih polj kota, razen "
"če ste popolnoma prepričani, da vaš nasprotnik ne bo mogel postaviti kamna "
"na vogal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sometimes it is better to offer some stones to your opponent."
msgstr "Včasih je bolje nasprotniku ponuditi nekaj kamnov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try to put stones on fields which prevent your opponent from moving."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite postaviti kamne na polja, ki vašemu nasprotniku preprečujejo "
"premikanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to force your opponent to put a stone in a neighboring field of a corner."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite prisiliti nasprotnika, da položi kamen v sosednje polje kota."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
