"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži najboljše rezultate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a dialog that displays different high score tables."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno, ki prikazuje različne tabele z najboljšimi rezultati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exit &kreversi;."
msgstr "Izhod &kreversi;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Removes your last move</action> as well as the computer's last move "
"from the board."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odstrani vašo zadnjo potezo</action> in zadnjo potezo računalnika s "
"plošče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hint</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>H</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Premakni</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Namig</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "The computer will <action>provide a hint for your next move.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Računalnik bo <action>posredoval namig za vašo naslednjo potezo.</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Last Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži zadnjo potezo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlights your opponent's last move."
msgstr "Osvetli nasprotnikovo zadnjo potezo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Legal Moves</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži zakonite poteze</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Highlights all the moves available</action> for your current move."
msgstr ""
"<action>Osvetli vse poteze, ki so na voljo</action> za vašo trenutno potezo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Move History</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži zgodovino premika</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables/Disables the move history sidebar."
msgstr "Omogoči/onemogoči stransko vrstico zgodovine premikanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Animation Speed</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Hitrost animacije</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>A submenu to set the game animation speed</action> between "
"<guimenuitem>Slow</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Normal</guimenuitem>, and "
"<guimenuitem>Fast</guimenuitem> options."
msgstr ""
"<action>Podmeni za nastavitev hitrosti animacije igre</action> med možnostmi "
"<guimenuitem>Počasi</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Normalno</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Hitro</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Use Colored Chips</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi barvne čipe</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle the color of the stones between black and white (default),</"
"action> and red and blue."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopi barvo kamnov med črno in belo (privzeto)</action> ter rdečo "
"in modro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Set the difficulty</action> from <guimenuitem>Very Easy</"
"guimenuitem> to <guimenuitem>Impossible</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Nastavite težavnost</action> z <guimenuitem>Zelo enostavno</"
"guimenuitem> na <guimenuitem>Nemogoče</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kreversi; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kreversi; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The only part of the game that can be changed is the color of the stones. To "
"change the color of the stones use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Use Colored Chips</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Edini del igre, ki ga je mogoče spremeniti, je barva kamnov. Če želite "
"spremeniti barvo kamnov, uporabite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi barvne "
"žetone</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kreversi; does not provide for the keyboard play."
msgstr "Ne. &kreversi; ne omogoča igranja s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kreversi; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. &kreversi; nima funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>."

